reviewText: Really great price, very good shots of the band, great sound quality. The advertisements for walmart inbetween each song were a bit annoying though, but still a good deal

yeah lol ok i was expecting more, but watching this is really awkward. fall out boy play five songs to an empty theater and the interview is only andy and pete. lol and when i say empty theater- oh yeah. no crowd what so ever, and you can hear every detail of the music being played, which is both good and bad. i love live in pheonix soooo much better, so i would recommend buying that instead :O
